{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Sets whether to show alert for push notifications when app is in foreground."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ ("},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:v","text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"text":"setShowPushnotificationAlert:","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@BOOL","text":"BOOL"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"show"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"name":"show","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"YES to show alerts in foreground, NO to suppress them (default)","type":"text"}]}]}]},{"content":[{"level":2,"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"By default, iOS does not display notification banners when the app is in the foreground."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"Enable this to show system notification alerts even when the app is active."}]},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Example","level":2,"text":"Example"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Configure based on app type:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"code":["class NotificationConfigManager {","","    func configureForAppType(_ appType: AppType) {","        switch appType {","        case .messaging:","            \/\/ Messaging apps typically handle notifications in-app","            Pushwoosh.configure.setShowPushnotificationAlert(false)","","        case .ecommerce, .news:","            \/\/ E-commerce and news apps benefit from showing all notifications","            Pushwoosh.configure.setShowPushnotificationAlert(true)","","        case .game:","            \/\/ Games might want to suppress during gameplay","            Pushwoosh.configure.setShowPushnotificationAlert(false)","        }","    }","","    func temporarilyDisableForegroundAlerts(during action: () -> Void) {","        let wasEnabled = Pushwoosh.configure.getShowPushnotificationAlert()","        Pushwoosh.configure.setShowPushnotificationAlert(false)","","        action()","","        Pushwoosh.configure.setShowPushnotificationAlert(wasEnabled)","    }","}"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"code":"UNUserNotificationCenterDelegate","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" and use "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Pushwoosh.ForegroundPush"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]}],"kind":"content"}],"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setShowPushnotificationAlert:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setshowpushnotificationalert:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"metadata":{"fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setShowPushnotificationAlert:"}],"modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)setShowPushnotificationAlert:","symbolKind":"method","title":"setShowPushnotificationAlert:","roleHeading":"Type Method","role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"setShowPushnotificationAlert:"}]},"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration/setShowPushnotificationAlert:":{"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"setShowPushnotificationAlert:","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setshowpushnotificationalert:","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setShowPushnoti